data.description:
Welcome to 404 Forster St!!! 

This charming house presents a wonderful opportunity for you to turn your dreams into reality. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 1 bathroom on the main floor, the possibilities are expanded with an unfinished basement, equipped with another bathroom. The unfinished basement serves as a blank canvas, offering limitless potential. You could transform it into additional bedrooms, create a cozy family room, or design an exciting game room - the choice is yours.

Outside, a spacious backyard is perfect for hosting family gatherings and outdoor entertainment. Nestled in a quiet and welcoming neighborhood, this home is just minutes away from beautiful downtown Farmington. This property is an ideal canvas for you to customize and create the home you've always envisioned.
